Create two new VMs, again unattendedly, which will then be Postgresql VMs. Use pgpool-II to set up master/master replication between them. 
Export the database from your Spacewalk server and import it into the new pgsql cluster. Reconfigure your Spacewalk instance to run off of that server.

https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/PostgreSQL
https://www.pgpool.net/mediawiki/index.php/Main_Page
https://www.a2hosting.com/kb/developer-corner/postgresql/import-and-export-a-postgresql-database
